thread.title: Ann-Catrin Karlgren

author: Ann-Catrin Karlgren
title: Ann-Catrin Karlgren
text: Easy and professional to deal with. Quick to help when contacted. And more important, very quick and helpful during breakdown assistance. The only reason for not marking 5 stars is that you cant change milage during policy as work location etc might change. Top ups are the only options and they are expensive. Policy milage is based on previous actual miles and bonus miles and I have found no way to amend those even at point of policy renewal
